            "title": "Timecom Tops Bursa Leaders As HLFG Slips Sharply",
            "description": "<div class=\"tdb-block-inner td-fix-index\">\n<p>Bursa Malaysia saw Timecom Bhd ([5031], TIMECOM) lead the top gainers today, rising 17 sen to RM5.72 with a volume of 1.945 million shares. \n\n\n\n</p><p>Other notable advancers included DLady Bhd ([3026], DLADY) up 12 sen to RM31.28 and KSSC Bhd ([5192], KSSC) adding 10.5 sen to RM0.915. </p><div class=\"g g-1\"><div class=\"g-dyn a-70 c-1\"></div></div>\n<p>Pineapple Bhd ([0006], PINEAPP) and KLCC REIT ([5235SS], KLCC) also recorded modest gains of 10 sen and 9 sen respectively.\n\n\n\n</p><p>On the losing side, Hong Leong Financial Group ([1082], HLFG) fell 1.30 to RM20.28 on 857,400 shares, marking the steepest decline of the day. \n\n\n\n</p><p>HEIM Bhd ([3255], HEIM) dropped 50 sen to RM22.50, while Hong Leong Bank ([5819], HLBANK) slipped 44 sen to RM23.86 on a volume of 2.943 million shares. \n\n\n\n</p><p>Allianz Malaysia ([1163], ALLIANZ) and F&amp;N Holdings ([3689], F&amp;N) were also among the top decliners, shedding 34 sen and 28 sen respectively.\n\n\n\n</p><p>The session reflected mixed market sentiment, with investors showing selective interest in technology and property-linked counters, while financial and consumer stocks underperformed.\n\n\n\n</p><h6 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Top Gainers</h6>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">No</th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Stock Name</th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Stock Code</th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Last Done</th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">CHG</th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">VOL (’00)</th></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">1</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://www.bursamalaysia.com/trade/trading_reso